citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:50 pm on
13-Sep-18.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 1:50 pm and called the licensee who was not available for the inspection. The
inspector then left the facility.
